      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i've checked the logs and the footage isn't showing much, which is what's weird. it feels like things are just... disappearing from the shelves when no one is looking. it's almost like they're being taken by something very small or something that knows exactly how to avoid the sensors. do you have any ideas on how to investigate \"invisible\" or highly stealthy theft patterns in a warehouse setting?",
