      "content": "If the visual evidence is lacking, you need to pivot your investigation to process and audit trails. Focus on discrepancies between system records and physical counts, particularly during stock movements. Look for patterns where small quantities of specific, high-value items vanish between receiving and putaway, or between picking and shipping. This suggests highly organized internal theft or sophisticated diversion tactics that bypass standard monitoring.",
